item.title: CVE-2019-10135|2024-08-04T22:10:09.963Z -- red%20hat -- osbs-client
item.description: A flaw was found in the yaml.load() function in the osbs-client versions since 0.46 before 0.56.1. Insecure use of the yaml.load() function allowed the user to load any suspicious object for code execution via the parsing of malicious YAML files.
